latestIgtvVideos.title: Here we go again... baby beluga fast forwarded!! Hahah ❤️
latestIgtvVideos.caption:
So, here’s a sped up video of some leg work I practiced this morning.
The last few months have brought up so many changes.
The good thing for me is that a lot of the inner work that I needed to focus on is being tapped into. They’re being pulled out from behind the curtain and as much as I hate it some days, it’s what I need the most.
Being impatient, hyper and too sensitive...among other things, are the few changes I am trying to bring about which has led to a bit of emotional eating that has made me put on some weight.
Having said that: it made me realise that we can all slip regardless of what path we are on or how aware we are.
For me: feeling good is important. The inner journey will always compliment the outer one.
Having people to talk to, taking one day at a time and being mindful about myself while trying to get used to taking care of myself fully, is top priority now.
It’s tough when you have a family or kids to look after and having yourself doing everything in this uncertain time can be very overwhelming.
Please reach out to people who can help or give you a listen.
I’m always here.
Let’s heal together.

Happy Sunday!!!!

latestPosts.caption:
When you feel a collapse, start with expanding your heart first.
Listen to it and feel your rhythm.

It’s not just a Yoga class.
It’s combined energy that makes it SO special.
We move, We dance, We play and laugh.
We stretch, we help and we push ourselves some days because we feel safe to!
Thank you for trusting me 🌸🤍

Take me back to the source
So my energy is restored
And my mind, clear.
Where my heart expands
And my mind rests
Where my being is balanced
And my mind, kind.
